com.wookler.zconfig.common.events

Class AbstractConfigUpdateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wookler.zconfig.common.events.AbstractConfigUpdateEvent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigServerUpdateEvent, ConfigUpdateEvent

    public abstract class AbstractConfigUpdateEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Update event structure for a configuration node update.

    Event Structure: 

          {
           "transaction" : [unique tnx ID],
           "group" : [application group],
           "application" : [application],
           "config" : [config name],
           "version" : [config version],
           "path" : [node path],
           "eventType" : [ADD/UPDATE/DELETE],
           "timestamp" : [timestamp]
       }
